		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694288070.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "My name is Meghana.\nAnd I can grant you renewed life."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694287632.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "A goddess..."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694288070.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Marta...\nYou had such great potential but were sadly cut short of reaching it.\nI know that you will do great things if you take my offer. \nThough, I would have a favor to ask of you in return…"
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694287632.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "A favor?"
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694288070.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Ah, you see my chapels have been plagued by vicious spirits recently, scaring off my disciples.\nThese spirits have crossed fully into the physical realm.\nNormally, I would take care of them myself, but I lack a physical form of my own to combat them.\nAlas, they are beyond my reach."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694287632.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "Well... I would like to help, but how am I supposed to deal with scary spirits?\nI was never able to talk to ghosts or anything before."
		},
		{
			"character": "character-1694288070.json",
			"event_id": "dialogic_001",
			"portrait": "",
			"text": "There are others in my world who have helped me in the past.\nMost didn't didn't think they were up to the task initially.\nBut I gifted them all [wave amp=10 freq=4]magical powers[/wave] and would do the same for you, Marta.\nThese powers would even be yours to keep."
		},
		{
			"animation": "pulse.gd",
			"animation_length": 0.3,
			"change_mirror_portrait": false,
			"change_position": false,
			"change_z_index": false,
